      "title": "Tomorrow's power outage details have been released",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has given permission to implement a 3-hour power cut tomorrow (24) as requested by the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "Accordingly, power cut will be enforced for 1 hour and 40 minutes from 1 pm to 6.30 pm and 1 hour and 20 minutes from 6.30 pm to 10.30 pm in 20 zones A to W."
      ],
